{"tid":2322502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"612一週年，民建聯刀手斬人；40歲手足唔交密碼，被警甴威脅「搞你老婆仔女」","createTime":"2020-12-12T11:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T12:01:50.000Z","uid":211994,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b171952483a64334433054396d6c1f53cf349973","tid":2322502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><strong>警甴暴行罄竹難書，下文記載之警暴事件僅為冰山一角，請移師至此頻道了解更多</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fneverforgivepopodklm&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=636d2266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">今日係12號</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"small\">只係揀咗幾單出嚟，實際12號仲有好多好多。最好就click入去望下啦，每一位手足都好重要㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fneverforgivepopodklm%2F646&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=088fe58b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/646</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n612：鄺星宇斬人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts/36440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frealtimenewsbroadcasts%2F36440&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=65c55d7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/realtimenewsbroadcasts/36440</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKBqYq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKBqYq2.jpg&h=98ed7ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jY0jire.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjY0jire.png&h=35284663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解當初唔咬實「民建聯刀手」呢件事唔放？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家冇人記得咁滯<br />\n<br />\n🟪🟥1012：九龍塘4義士。26歲曾、30歲黃、鄭、40歲黃。曾還押至今270日。40歲黃被威嚇唔交密碼會「搞佢老婆仔女」<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aN1vu8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aN1vu8&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=8831256b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aN1vu8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F7866&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=55c96169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/7866</a><br />\n<br />\n🟥812：機場少女被殺人犯非禮拔槍，23歲灰衫葉義士救人被暴動，還押至今420日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F4227&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=b5dd45d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4227</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2xdoUHi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xdoUHi&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c9ba997c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2xdoUHi</a><br />\n你地拍手歡呼食花生就開心，義士還押到而家👆<br />\n<br />\n🛑🟥812：機場28歲何被捕兩次（825元朗）愛犬送去愛協，還押至今420日。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/15280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F15280&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c911f276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/15280</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2xmwcYH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xmwcYH&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=05f88f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2xmwcYH</a><br />\n<br />\n🟪🟨1112：西營盤18歲吳錄口供前，被狗手持胡椒恐嚇「想唔想試下？」守行為兩年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4344\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F4344&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=9b3e9993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/4344</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>屌你老味投完票又唔見人</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🟨🛑1112：澳洲籍32歲女義士被捕兩次，114中環破壞民賤聯海報罰款$2000。1112中環襲狗判監三個月。上庭前話知道有40人（被捕組投票）撐佢好開心，結果現實得個位數，上庭知道要判監淒厲地嚎哭，喊到刪咗門都聽到，患病媽媽聽到對女兒不利既消息後係咁咳，送車得10人（529）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F5485&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=e1782dbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/5485</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bOzliV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bOzliV&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=dae4d936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bOzliV</a><br />\n<br />\n🟪🛑1112：中環26歲義士在狗屋，被2狗按肩膀及頸側身推向牆1分鐘，威嚇「咁樣唔驚啊，陣間就再驚啲！」另外，A14鄭（22）另有暴動私了案‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9773&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=a5645066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9773</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10141\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10141&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=58f7d24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10141</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝「香港自殺報道資料庫」<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2FHKSuicide&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2e4e9b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide</a><br />\n被捕組時間表<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psqNvm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psqNvm&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jco429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=ff442564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psqNvm</a><br />\n、實時、scott、被捕組總台、直播台、搜證台、收信台、資訊台、失蹤組。"},{"pid":"adfc2923e4407bbae4ce08ed8018885423e06d79","tid":2322502,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8ed72428b6d33544639d34ad5568151b21dbf7","tid":2322502,"uid":211994,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"法院要人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0U8bMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0U8bMW.jpg&h=37d993da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d6921794c4d6036c6d466d611607e8cd9661f6a","tid":2322502,"uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:14:23.000Z","msg":"當年今日系列<br />\n<br />\n1號<br />\n［當年今日］呢一個月嘅每一日，我都會同大家重溫一次警甴暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2號<br />\n［每日警暴回顧］3月2號，15歲手足被警甴虐至耳朵失聰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308157</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3號<br />\n［當年今日］11月3號，曱甴叫學生記者除褲：「新屋嶺雞姦好好玩」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2309702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2309702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n4號<br />\n［警暴回顧］11月4號，義士為救護車開路救周梓樂，被狗爆頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2311446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2311446</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n5號<br />\nEL2892陳錦權，係咪以為自己開車撞完手足冇人記得？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2312655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2312655</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n6號<br />\n手足被曱甴扑頭，眼鏡跌落地，狗立刻踩碎鏡片話「依家無啦」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2313991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2313991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n7號<br />\n大埔墟站屠殺。中六生滿地腦漿，患創傷後遺症，被逼放棄今屆公開試。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2315409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2315409</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8號<br />\n19歲韓手足，狗車被男狗掌摑辱罵恐嚇「信唔信我係度強姦你？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2316821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2316821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n9號<br />\n［有圖有片］多隻警甴圍毆叔叔，扑頭成地血，弱智警甴用口罩接觸傷口止血<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2318450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2318450</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n10號<br />\n831翻版，封商場至少十幾個鐘；黑色母親節，被襲記者反被控<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2319727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2319727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n11號<br />\n黃埔25歲張被逼臉貼地，膝頭壓臉踩臉爆耳流血，狗車被圍毆大力揑下體，被丫叉橡膠射禁送院。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2321161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2321161</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n12號<br />\n612一週年，民建聯刀手斬人；40歲手足唔交密碼，被警甴威脅「搞你老婆仔女」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2322502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2322502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ac804ca7e71f2236a771c85d0430afee1809c86","tid":2322502,"uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><p class=\"center\">YOU NEVER WALK ALONE.<br />\n<br />\n香港人係痛苦嘅共同體，我地因感受到彼此嘅痛苦而團結互相扶持。香港人要報仇，請先學會做一個記仇嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n但如需心理及情緒支援，以下有好多人可以幫到你㗎<br />\n<br />\n好好休息下再歸隊啦。<br />\n<br />\n</p><br />\n*請廣傳*<br />\n以下係一D情緒支援服務資料（不斷更新，歡迎更正、更新）：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612/3801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fre